dc_title_s: Provinciae Cantii: vulgo Kendt nova descriptio.; Province of Kent
dc_creator_sm: Jansson, Jan, 1588-1664. Appendix Atlas.,Vignaud, Henry, 1830-1922, former owner.
dc_description_s: Relief shown pictorially. Includes illustrations of ships and sea monsters in the ocean. Does not match any states listed in Van der Krogt. From the Jansson Appendix Atlas 1636-1680, title created to represent a unique collection within the Clark Library, University of Michigan. 1 map; 37 x 49 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
